Tolong jaga adikmu.

00:17:39.320 --> 00:17:40.280
Lakshmi.

00:17:41.040 --> 00:17:42.000
Saya akan kembali.

00:17:47.240 --> 00:17:49.240
Lakshmi, kamu baik-baik saja?

